Process called "create_language_info_database" returns Dictionary[String, LanguageInfo]:
    Note: Create language information database
    Let languages be dictionary containing Let english be LanguageInfo with:
    language_code as "en"
    english_name as "English"
    native_name as "English"
    iso_639_1 as Some with value as "en"
    iso_639_2 as Some with value as "eng"
    iso_639_3 as "eng"
    language_family as "Germanic"
    writing_systems as list containing "Latn"
    speaker_count as 1500000000
    official_territories as list containing "US", "GB", "CA", "AU", "NZ"
    pluralization_type as "simple"
    metadata as dictionary containing Set languages at key "en" to english Return languages

